<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Thailand Honeymoon</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="country-hero-honey" style="background: url('/img/pexels-pixabay-208444.jpg');">
    <h1>Thailand Honeymoon</h1>
    <p>Exotic adventures, serene beaches, and unforgettable moments</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Description -->
  <section class="country-description-honey">
    <p>
      Thailand offers a perfect blend of vibrant culture, stunning landscapes, and luxurious experiences, making it an ideal honeymoon destination. From bustling cities to tranquil islands, every couple can find their paradise here.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Attractions -->
  <section class="attractions-honey">
    <h2>Most Popular Honeymoon Places in Thailand</h2>
    <div class="attraction-grid-honey">

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/47dcbf64ee9ceca1652be1d1f0e94b3f.jpg" alt="Phuket">
        <h3>Phuket</h3>
        <p>Thailand's largest island, known for its beautiful beaches, vibrant nightlife, and luxury resorts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/e747a6560fd7b28f2887bdb0b4531525.jpg" alt="Chiang Mai">
        <h3>Chiang Mai</h3>
        <p>A cultural haven in northern Thailand, offering temples, mountain landscapes, and unique experiences.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/b6be7078798fbe79479a76d61d91a410.jpg" alt="Krabi">
        <h3>Krabi</h3>
        <p>Home to stunning limestone cliffs, clear waters, and secluded beaches, perfect for romance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/a41495c6df655176952904fa65c53422.jpg" alt="Koh Samui">
        <h3>Koh Samui</h3>
        <p>An island paradise offering luxury resorts, palm-fringed beaches, and vibrant nightlife.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/bbe6daf00ff8db952f16bc8cfa6afb67.jpg" alt="Khao Lak">
        <h3>Khao Lak</h3>
        <p>A peaceful coastal area with pristine beaches and close proximity to national parks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/82e3ec7fe5c238fcd339c77101e5cef4.jpg" alt="Phi Phi Islands">
        <h3>Phi Phi Islands</h3>
        <p>Famous for their crystal-clear waters, dramatic cliffs, and vibrant marine life.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hotels -->
  <section class="hotels-honey">
    <h2>Romantic Stays in Thailand</h2>
    <div class="hotel-grid-honey">

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/e7b3f42d903c215ed2fd7103650a2ca1.jpg" alt="Amanpuri, Phuket">
        <h3>Amanpuri, Phuket</h3>
        <p>A luxury resort offering private villas, serene beaches, and exceptional service.</p>
        <a href="https://www.aman.com/resorts/amanpuri" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/20ed99d7dbea66be093925fcd8974541.jpg" alt="Phulay Bay, a Ritz-Carlton Reserve">
        <h3>Phulay Bay, a Ritz-Carlton Reserve</h3>
        <p>An exclusive retreat in Krabi, featuring spacious villas and personalized experiences.</p>
        <a href="https://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/phulay-bay" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/97ee0cd179f88c2ce6399be0946c5be1.jpg" alt="Six Senses Yao Noi">
        <h3>Six Senses Yao Noi</h3>
        <p>A sustainable luxury resort offering panoramic views and private pool villas.</p>
        <a href="https://www.sixsenses.com/en/resorts/yao-noi" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/d843d40c530db593505fbad2fc883651.jpg" alt="Rayavadee Krabi">
        <h3>Rayavadee Krabi</h3>
        <p>Set between lush cliffs and the sea, this secluded beachfront resort offers tropical pavilions, a famous cave dining experience, and pure romantic luxury.</p>
        <a href="https://www.rayavadee.com" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/02b435fded2284be911cc0b4f19d5478.jpg" alt="Anantara Chiang Mai Resort">
        <h3>Anantara Chiang Mai Resort</h3>
        <p>A riverside retreat blending modern luxury with traditional Thai elements.</p>
        <a href="https://www.anantara.com/en/chiang-mai" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/494f1b5ec20f97784a3d70af255a7ee3.jpg" alt="The Slate Phuket">
        <h3>The Slate Phuket</h3>
        <p>An art-inspired luxury resort near a tranquil beach in Phuket, offering creative villa designs, lush gardens, and truly unique romantic experiences.</p>
        <a href="https://www.theslatephuket.com" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>            

    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
